    section
      .wrapper
        .columns.reverse
          .content
            h2 The ultimate comparison of UX industry tools.
            p There's a new design tool every week. What's the difference? See how these design, prototyping, collaboration, and monitoring tools work for you.
            a(href="/tools")
              button.blue See the Tools 
               include img/icons/arrow-right.svg
          .content
            a(href="/tools")
              .landing-image
                img(src="img/landing-image-logos.png" alt="App Logos")
                img.shadow-image(src="img/bottom-shadow.png")

    section
      .wrapper
        .columns
          .content
            a(href="/library")
              .landing-image
                img(src="img/landing-image-books.png" alt="App Logos")
                img.shadow-image(src="img/bottom-shadow.png")
          .content
            h2 The ultimate list of UX industry books.
            p What's everyone reading these days? Itâ€™s hard to know where to start in a big industry like UX design. See the most popular and recommended books in the industry.
            a(href="/library")
              button.blue Browse the Library
